    </release>
    <release version="0.1.25" date="2026-06-24">
      <description>
        <ul>
          <li>Polish recurring rows with colored priority letters, occurrence-date child rows, and consistent indentation.</li>
          <li>Allow recurring template subprojects to change while keeping the main project fixed.</li>
          <li>Show only the schedule controls relevant to the selected recurrence type.</li>
