          <li>Separate recurring templates from normal todos with Daily, Weekly, and Monthly template controls.</li>
          <li>Show generated recurring instances as children while keeping template deletion and generated-instance edits safe.</li>
          <li>Keep recurring calendar events aligned with generated, completed, and deleted instances.</li>
