        <ul>
          <li>Show counted parent-overwrite warnings under Priority or Due date.</li>
          <li>Block child due dates before their parent and keep duplicate todos editable as new templates.</li>
          <li>Keep dependency graph nesting separate for active and completed todos.</li>
        </ul>
      </description>
    </release>
    <release version="0.1.17" date="2026-06-23">
      <description>
        <ul>
          <li>Make existing todo dependencies read-only in the editor.</li>
          <li>Simplify parent child-constraint warnings and cascade child updates on save.</li>
          <li>Keep the priority dropdown model stable while editing parent priorities.</li>
        </ul>
      </description>
    </release>
    <release version="0.1.16" date="2026-06-23">
      <description>
        <ul>
          <li>Keep unavailable dependency priority choices visible while preventing selection.</li>
          <li>Normalize duplicated due-date text produced by calendar/default prefill paths.</li>
          <li>Use timer-style summaries in dependency search results.</li>
          <li>Show inline dependency adjustment and child-constraint warnings in the todo editor.</li>
        </ul>
      </description>
    </release>
    <release version="0.1.15" date="2026-06-23">
