        <ul>
          <li>Move dependency graph rendering behind a Project order setting.</li>
          <li>Use a searchable parent selector and constrain child priority/due choices.</li>
          <li>Warn before parent edits break children, with an option to update children.</li>
          <li>Fix dependency due-date validation and calendar date selection.</li>
