          <li>Add a Depends order mode with collapsible dependency graph rows by subproject.</li>
          <li>Make dependency selection searchable and clamp priority/due choices inside dependency constraints.</li>
          <li>Correct dependency priority validation so dependents cannot outrank their dependency.</li>
        </ul>
      </description>
    </release>
    <release version="0.1.13" date="2026-06-23">
