          <li>Validate dependency priority, due-date order, and circular chains before saving todos.</li>
          <li>Prefer newly unblocked dependent todos after completing their dependency.</li>
          <li>Sort tied todos by dependency chain and creation order instead of alphabetically.</li>
          <li>Remove calendar events when dated todos become completed.</li>
        </ul>
      </description>
    </release>
    <release version="0.1.12" date="2026-06-23">
      <description>
