          <li>Add optional todo dependencies stored as hidden dep:id metadata.</li>
          <li>Remember todo defaults by project, including due-date reuse with past-date clamping.</li>
          <li>Add a native shortcuts dialog and stricter subproject input rules.</li>
        </ul>
